	* Makefile.am, VERSION.av, configure.ac, shlib-import, shlib.in:
	  `source shlib' will receive the arguments passed to the script.
	  This is unwanted.

	  . shlib won't accept any argument more, it's only load
	  import-feature.

	  So, a new shlib-import should be used for one-line import.

